                  initial term
                
                +
                
                  last term
                
                )
                .
              
            
          
        
      
    
    {\displaystyle {\begin{aligned}S_{n}&={\frac {n}{2}}[a+a+(n-1)d].\\&={\frac {n}{2}}(a+a_{n}).\\&={\frac {n}{2}}({\text{initial term}}+{\text{last term}}).\end{aligned}}}
  Furthermore, the mean value of the series can be calculated via: 
  
    
      
        
          S
          
            n
          
        
        
          /
        
        n
      
    
    {\displaystyle S_{n}/n}
  :

  
    
      
        
          
            a
            ¯
          
        
