  for positive integers 
  
    
      
        m
      
    
    {\displaystyle m}
   and 
  
    
      
        n
      
    
    {\displaystyle n}
   is given by

  
    
      
        
          
            
              n
              !
            
            
              (
              m
              −
              1
              )
              !
            
          
        
        .
      
    
    {\displaystyle {\frac {n!}{(m-1)!}}.}

